uint32_t DPC_ObjectDetection_Stats_t::subFramePreparationCycles

Sub frame preparation cycles. Note when this is reported as part of the process result reporting, then it indicates the cycles that took place in the previous sub-frame/frame for preparing to switch to the sub-frame that is being reported because switching happens in the processing of DPC_OBJDET_IOCTL__DYNAMIC_EXECUTE_RESULT_EXPORTED, which is after the DPC process.
